Typealiases.html#/s:17MetovaJSONCodable3.name: JSONCustomDateFormatterCodable
Typealiases.html#/s:17MetovaJSONCodable3.abstract: Type alias for conforming to JSONCustomDateFormatterDecodable & JSONCustomDateFormatterEncodable. The same way Codable is a type alias for Decodable & Encodable

Typealiases.html#/s:17MetovaJSONCodable0.name: JSONCodable
Typealiases.html#/s:17MetovaJSONCodable0.abstract: Type alias for conforming to JSONDecodable & JSONEncodable. The same way Codable is a type alias for Decodable & Encodable

Typealiases.html#/s:17MetovaJSONCodable4.name: JSON
Typealiases.html#/s:17MetovaJSONCodable4.abstract: Type alias added for use as a shorthand json dictionary objects

Protocols/JSONEncodable.html#/s:17Metova.name: jsonEncoder
Protocols/JSONEncodable.html#/s:17Metova.abstract: Deafult JSONEncoder. This is mainly to be used by child protocols that need custom encoders

Protocols/JSONDecodable.html#/s:17Metova.name: jsonDecoder
Protocols/JSONDecodable.html#/s:17Metova.abstract: Default JSONDecoder. This is mainly to be used by child protocols that need custom decoders

Protocols/JSONCustomDateFormatterEncodab.name: dateFormatter
Protocols/JSONCustomDateFormatterEncodab.abstract: Customizeable date formatter. This will need to be implemented by conforming objects

Protocols/JSONCustomDateFormatterDecodab.name: dateFormatter
Protocols/JSONCustomDateFormatterDecodab.abstract: Customizeable date formatter. This will need to be implemented by conforming objects

Protocols/JSONEpochDateDecodable.html.name: JSONEpochDateDecodable
Protocols/JSONEpochDateDecodable.html.abstract: JSONDecodable child protocol with support for dates as timestamps

Protocols/JSONEpochDateEncodable.html.name: JSONEpochDateEncodable
Protocols/JSONEpochDateEncodable.html.abstract: JSONEncodable child protocol with support for dates as timestamps

Protocols/JSONCustomDateFormatterDecodab.name: JSONCustomDateFormatterDecodable
Protocols/JSONCustomDateFormatterDecodab.abstract: JSONDecodable child protocol that allows the user to define a cust dateFormatter. There is no default dateFormatter defined here so any object conforming to the protocol will need to add this

Protocols/JSONCustomDateFormatterEncodab.name: JSONCustomDateFormatterEncodable
Protocols/JSONCustomDateFormatterEncodab.abstract: JSONEncodable child protocol that allows the user to define a cust dateFormatter. There is no default dateFormatter defined here so any object conforming to the protocol will need to add this

Protocols/JSONDecodable.html.name: JSONDecodable
Protocols/JSONDecodable.html.abstract: JSONDecodable protocol with an init for JSON. Conforms to Decodable protocol

Protocols/JSONEncodable.html.name: JSONEncodable
Protocols/JSONEncodable.html.abstract: JSONEncodable protocol for easily getting a JSON object from a conforming JSONCodable object. Conforms to Encodable protocol
